# =============================================================================
# ASTRO APP — CLIENT (Expo) ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# Copy this file to .env:
#   cp .env.example .env
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# REQUIRED — Backend API URL
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Web browser / iOS simulator:
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

# Physical phone (Expo Go) — use your PC's LAN IP instead of localhost:
# Find IP: ipconfig (Windows) → look for IPv4 Address
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.5:5000/api
#
# Note: If left as localhost, the app auto-detects your PC IP on Expo Go.
# Only set manually if auto-detection doesn't work.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# GMAIL OTP — configured on SERVER, not here
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Real email OTP is sent from server/.env using these keys:
#   SMTP_USER, SMTP_PASS, SMTP_FROM, OTP_EXPIRY_MINUTES, APP_NAME
# See server/.env.example for full setup instructions.